title: Babybel Cheese 18 Count Variety Pack | Babybel®
text: NEW! Introducing the ultimate snacking sensation: The 18-count Variety Pack of Mini Babybel® Cheese! Packed with flavor and convenience, this assortment is designed to satisfy every craving. Each pack features an irresistible selection of Babybel’s iconic mini cheeses, each encased in our signature red wax coating. Mini Babybel® cheese snacks are ideal for tossing into lunchboxes, packing for picnics, or enjoying straight from the fridge whenever hunger strikes. This Variety Pack contains: 8 x Original 5 x Monterey Jack Variety 5 x White Cheddar Variety Each Mini Babybel® cheese snack offers 4g of Protein and is a good source of calcium*. Learn more about Babybel® calories and nutritional information below. *See nutritional information for saturated fat content.
